Flag llvm
 Description: Build with llvm backend
 Default: false

Flag llvm_static
  Description: Links with llvm in a static mode
  Default: true


Library bap_llvm
  Path:          lib/bap_llvm
  Build$:        flag(everything) || flag(llvm)
  BuildDepends:  bap, ogre, monads, core_kernel, ppx_jane, mmap
  FindlibName:   bap-llvm
  Modules:       Bap_llvm,
                 Bap_llvm_loader
  InternalModules:
                 Bap_llvm_config,
                 Bap_llvm_disasm
  CCOpt:         $cc_optimization
  CCLib:         $llvm_lib $cxxlibs $llvm_ldflags -lcurses
  CSources:      llvm_disasm.h,
                 llvm_disasm.c,
                 llvm_stubs.c,
                 llvm_error_or.c,
                 llvm_error_or.h,
                 llvm_loader.c,
                 llvm_loader.h,
